name: American Flag Paracord Bracelets
description:
Show your patriotism with these cute red, white & blue parachute cord bracelets!!

Each bracelet is made by hand, using 7 strand, 550 paracord (made in the USA), with a 3/8" curved side release clasp. 

I don't burn the ends, as you'll find with most paracord bracelets.  

Customize yours by choosing  your own clasp color (red, white, or blue). 

The clasp length is included in the total length of the bracelet. 

Prices range from $6.99-$9.99 depending on length/size. 

NOTE: If you'd like to change the knot style (cobra or saw tooth) and/or clasp color (red, white or blue), just contact me after you place your order specifying the changes to be made. :)
